<title>USA: Caere authorizes share buyback.</title>
<headline>Caere authorizes share buyback.</headline>
<dateline>LOS GATOS, Calif. 1997-04-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Caere Corp said its board of directors recently authorized the repurchase of up to one million shares of its common stock, to be made from time to time on the open market.</p>
<p>It said the shares it purchases will be held for issuance in connection with future exercises of employee stock options and for use in the employee stock purchase plan.</p>
